"{\"uid\": \"baltictimes.com-olympic_casino_should_have_stopped_stepukonis_from_gambling___body\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"VILNIUS - Virginijus Dauksys, head of Lithuania's Gaming Control Authority, says the watchdog is currently checking whether Olympic Casino Group Baltija complied with all the requirements as Sarunas Stepukonis, a former partner at BaltCap Infrastructure Fund, is suspected of having gambled away at least 27 million euros at casinos.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 333, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 38, \"end\": 47, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.8054119134748077e-12, \"text\": \"Lithuania\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania\"}, {\"begin\": 132, \"end\": 144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Groupe_Casino\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Casino Group\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Groupe_Casino\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Groupe_Casino\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"VILNIUS - Virginijus Dauksys\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 28}, {\"ngram\": \"head\", \"from\": 30, \"to\": 34}, {\"ngram\": \"the watchdog\", \"from\": 81, \"to\": 93}, {\"ngram\": \"all the requirements\", \"from\": 167, \"to\": 187}, {\"ngram\": \"Sarunas Stepukonis\", \"from\": 191, \"to\": 209}, {\"ngram\": \"a former partner\", \"from\": 211, \"to\": 227}, {\"ngram\": \"BaltCap Infrastructure Fund\", \"from\": 231, \"to\": 258}, {\"ngram\": \"at least 27 million euros\", \"from\": 296, \"to\": 321}, {\"ngram\": \"casinos\", \"from\": 325, \"to\": 332}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dauksys acknowledges that Stepukonis' gambling was \\\"potentially problematic\\\" and that Olympic Casino should have stopped it.\", \"from\": 335, \"to\": 459, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dauksys\", \"from\": 335, \"to\": 342}, {\"ngram\": \"Stepukonis' gambling\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 381}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic Casino\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 435}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He pointed out that the gambling watchdog issued guidelines for 2021 and 2023 to be followed by gambling operators in cases of problem gambling, but they are only of a recommendatory nature.\", \"from\": 461, \"to\": 651, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gambling watchdog\", \"from\": 481, \"to\": 502}, {\"ngram\": \"guidelines\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 520}, {\"ngram\": \"gambling operators\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 575}, {\"ngram\": \"cases\", \"from\": 579, \"to\": 584}, {\"ngram\": \"problem gambling\", \"from\": 588, \"to\": 604}, {\"ngram\": \"a recommendatory nature\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 650}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Unfortunately, they are only recommendations.\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 699, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"only recommendations\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 698}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They define a lot of mechanisms on what a gambling operator should do.\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 770, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 717}, {\"ngram\": \"mechanisms\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 731}, {\"ngram\": \"a gambling operator\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If he gambled on such huge amounts, they should have come into contact with the gambler and prevent the gambling,\\\" Dauksys said.\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 899, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such huge amounts\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 805}, {\"ngram\": \"contact\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 841}, {\"ngram\": \"the gambler\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 858}, {\"ngram\": \"the gambling\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 883}, {\"ngram\": \"Dauksys\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 893}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Olympic's CEO has said that they followed all the rules, so we will look into that too.\\\"\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 989, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic's CEO\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 914}, {\"ngram\": \"all the rules\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 956}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For his part, Rolandas Kiskis, head of the Financial Crime Investigation Service, says his service has not received a single report of suspicious transactions from Olympic Casino, and, in general, the service has received between three and five such reports from gambling companies over the last three years.\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1299, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1034, \"end\": 1071, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Financial_Crime_Investigation_Service\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Financial Crime Investigation Service\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Financial_Crime_Investigation_Service\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Financial_Crime_Investigation_Service\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his part\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1003}, {\"ngram\": \"Rolandas Kiskis\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1020}, {\"ngram\": \"head\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1026}, {\"ngram\": \"his service\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1089}, {\"ngram\": \"a single report\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1122}, {\"ngram\": \"suspicious transactions\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1149}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic Casino\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1169}, {\"ngram\": \"the service\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1199}, {\"ngram\": \"between three and five such reports\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1248}, {\"ngram\": \"gambling companies\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1272}, {\"ngram\": \"the last three years\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1298}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He did not say how much money Stepukonis may have gambled away, nor did he comment on whether there might have been other ways the money was embezzled.\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1452, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"how much money\", \"from\": 1316, \"to\": 1330}, {\"ngram\": \"Stepukonis\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1341}, {\"ngram\": \"other ways\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1427}, {\"ngram\": \"the money\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1437}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Hypothetically, we can come up with a lot of versions here and we are checking them, I will certainly not speculate,\\\" Kiskis said.\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1585, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1496}, {\"ngram\": \"versions\", \"from\": 1500, \"to\": 1508}, {\"ngram\": \"Kiskis\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1579}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to the FCIS, if a gambling organizer failed to comply with the anti-money laundering requirements and prevent such operations, it could face a fine of up to 1.1 million euros.\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1772, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the FCIS\", \"from\": 1600, \"to\": 1608}, {\"ngram\": \"a gambling organizer\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1633}, {\"ngram\": \"the anti-money laundering requirements\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1694}, {\"ngram\": \"such operations\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1722}, {\"ngram\": \"a fine\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1744}, {\"ngram\": \"up to 1.1 million euros\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1771}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked whether the authorities are looking into the possibility that the gambling company was not only a service provider but also participated in the money laundering scheme, Kiskis said that \\\"this possibility is also being assessed\\\".\", \"from\": 1774, \"to\": 2008, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the authorities\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1803}, {\"ngram\": \"the possibility\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1836}, {\"ngram\": \"the gambling company\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1862}, {\"ngram\": \"not only a service provider\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 1894}, {\"ngram\": \"the money laundering scheme\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 1947}, {\"ngram\": \"Kiskis\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 1955}, {\"ngram\": \"this possibility\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1983}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Commenting on Olympic Casino's role in this story, he said that Stepukonis is the only suspect in this case yet.\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2122, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic Casino's role\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2045}, {\"ngram\": \"this story\", \"from\": 2049, \"to\": 2059}, {\"ngram\": \"Stepukonis\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2084}, {\"ngram\": \"the only suspect\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2104}, {\"ngram\": \"this case\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2117}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dauksys says the FCIS will be informed after the investigation and if any suspicions about Olympic Casino emerge.\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2237, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dauksys\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2131}, {\"ngram\": \"the FCIS\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2145}, {\"ngram\": \"the investigation\", \"from\": 2169, \"to\": 2186}, {\"ngram\": \"any suspicions\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2208}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic Casino emerge\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please enter your username and password.\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2279, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your username\", \"from\": 2252, \"to\": 2265}, {\"ngram\": \"password\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2278}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A subscription to The Baltic Times is a cost-effective way of staying in touch with the latest Baltic news and views enabling you full access from anywhere with an Internet connection.Subscribe Now!\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2479, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2299, \"end\": 2315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Baltic_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Baltic Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Baltic_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Baltic_Times\"}, {\"begin\": 2376, \"end\": 2382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baltic_states\", \"score\": 0.9999999996978204, \"rank\": 1.53